- RandomX commitments with double-hashing #265
- Invalidate CPU I-cache on Apple Silicon #259

issue.title: `randomx_reciprocal` is slow
issue.body:
This function is not optimized:

https://github.com/tevador/RandomX/blob/d3c96482eeb1a99f1da38a0ada82d282619c8eb4/src/reciprocal.c#L47-L72

There is an optimized version inside the ARM64 JIT compiler implemented by @SChernykh . It would be better to optimize `randomx_reciprocal` rather than duplicating the code inline.
